_sText:
The map was created on February 6, 2010 

This is a modification of the map zm_lila_panic. 
The map has more space and shelters from zombies, also added a 12-story house (the last 2 floors - attic).  In the house go to the top floor and go on the long bridges, a lot of spawn player points, so you can play both on the map 64 and online.

There is 2 version of this map and it is 100% better, prettier and even big than this one! And with normal lighting.
